tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  15,95,"Wata a ɗenƴo ɓe. Menen Men heediii ma e pewje jalkitooɓe jeyaaɓe e ardiiɓe heeferɓe Qurayshi ɓen."
  15,96,"Ɓen waɗtidooɓe e Alla reweteeɗo goo. Aray ka ɓe annda wattannde bone sirku maɓɓe on."
  15,99,"Duumo-ɗaa e rewugol Joomi maa fotde hiɗa wuuri haa maayde nden tawe e ɗum."
  16,1,"Ko Alla ñaawi kon leptirgol onon heeferɓe ɓen ɓadike. Wata on hawjan ɗum ado hewtude. Senayee woodanii Alla e kon sirkooɓe ɓen kafidata Mo e mun."